<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Equipment Used</h2>
<p class="text-gray-400 mb-6">Professional paranormal investigation tools are provided — you'll learn how to use each one. Guests are welcome to bring their own equipment as well.</p>
<div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-14">

  <div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-5">
    <div class="text-purple-400 font-semibold mb-1">Spirit Box (P-SB7)</div>
    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Scans the FM and AM bands along with high-frequency white noise, where spirit voices can seemingly form words.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-5">
    <div class="text-purple-400 font-semibold mb-1">EMF Detector</div>
    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Entities are said to emit electromagnetic energy — this device detects unexplained fluctuations in electromagnetic fields.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-5">
    <div class="text-purple-400 font-semibold mb-1">REM Pod</div>
    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Emits its own electromagnetic field and signals any disruptions that enter that field.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-5">
    <div class="text-purple-400 font-semibold mb-1">Thermal Camera</div>
    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Measures the temperature of objects and entities in the room — including the ones you cannot see.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-5">
    <div class="text-purple-400 font-semibold mb-1">Digital Voice Recorder</div>
    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Used to capture voices or sounds that may not be audible in the moment — reviewed after the session.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-5">
    <div class="text-purple-400 font-semibold mb-1">Cat Balls</div>
    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Yes, cat balls. These motion-activated cat toys light up when touched — by someone, or something. A paranormal investigation staple.</p>
  </div>

</div>

